snippet.title: Sister Lumina and the Hypnosis Cult - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
When Lumina is forced to open a forbidden book passed down by her grandmother in order to rescue her best friend, she will have to pay a hefty price to gain the power to free her and ensure her safety.
